Package: jointest
Version: 2.0
Date: 2024-11-15
Title: Multivariate testing through joint resampling-based tests
Author: Livio Finos and Angela Andreella
Maintainer: Livio Finos <livio.finos@unipd.it>
Description: Runs resampling-based tests jointly (e.g., sign-flip score tests <doi.org/10.1111/rssb.12369>) to allow for multivariate testing, i.e., weak and strong control of the Familywise Error Rate or True Discovery Proportion.
Imports: flipscores, dplyr, magrittr, flip, stats, graphics, grDevices
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL-2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: logistf
Remotes: livioivil/flipscores
